title: Eidolon Transcendence
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Your connection with your eidolon approaches its peak, granting your eidolon access to a powerful new ability depending on its type, as described in Eidolon Abilities in each eidolon’s entry. 

This ability also increases one of the eidolon’s ability scores by 2.